data.description:
This charming single-family home spans 1,434 square feet and offers 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom with original hardwood floors, offering an open floor plan,
ready for your personal touch. Experience the updated kitchen and bathroom and other delightful features that are a must-see. Situated in a prime location,
this home provides both comfort and convenience-well-maintained property, perfect for first-time homebuyers or those looking to downsize. With a spacious
backyard, complemented by a detached garage, ideal for entertaining friends and family. See it before it's gone!
